  <extension point="xbmc.addon.metadata">
    <summary lang="en_GB">Watch Pokémon TV</summary>
    <description lang="en_GB">
      This addon allows you watch Pokémon TV with Kodi. It uses the offical API https://www.pokemon.com/api/pokemontv/v2/channels/us/ as used by https://watch.pokemon.com .
      
