      The applicable TOS may vary based on your location.
    </disclaimer>
    <language>el dk es fi fr de it nl no br ru se uk us</language>
    <platform>all</platform>
    <license>GPL-3.0-only</license>
    <source>https://github.com/SyrupThinker/kodi-pokemon-tv/</source>
    <news>v0.1.0 (2020-03-22)
    Initial version.
